library(raster)
library(tidyverse)
library(ggthemes)
library(patchwork)
library(maptools)
library(ggmap)
library(marmap)
usa <- map_data(map= "state")
usa
us_missouri <- map_data(map = "state",
                        region = "missouri")
us_missouri
us_other <- subset(x = usa,
subset = region %in% c("alabama",
"florida",
"mississippi",
"north carolina"))
us_other
ggplot() + 
  geom_polygon(data = us_other, 
               aes(x = long, 
                   y = lat, 
                   group = group), 
               fill = "gray")

ggplot() +
geom_polygon(data = us_other,
aes(x = long,
y = lat,
group = group),
fill = "gray") +
geom_polygon(data = us_missouri,
aes(x = long, y = lat,
group = group),
fill = "black")

ggplot() +
geom_polygon(data = us_other,
aes(x = long,
y = lat,
group = group),
fill = "gray") +
geom_polygon(data = us_missouri,
aes(x = long, y = lat,
group = group),
fill = "black") +
geom_polygon(data = usa,
aes(x=long,
y = lat,
group = group),
fill = NA,
color = "black")

us_map <- ggplot() +
geom_polygon(data = us_other,
aes(x = long,
y = lat,
group = group),
fill = "gray") +
geom_polygon(data = us_missouri,
aes(x = long, y = lat,
group = group),
fill = "black") +
geom_polygon(data = usa,
aes(x=long,
y = lat,
group = group),
fill = NA,
color = "black") +
theme_map() +
coord_fixed(1.3)
us_map

missouri <- map_data("county", "missouri")
mo_scott <- subset(missouri, subregion %in% c("scott"))
mo_map <- ggplot() +
geom_polygon(data = missouri, aes(x=long, y = lat, group = group), fill = NA, color = "black") +
geom_polygon(data = mo_scott, aes(x = long, y = lat, group = group), fill = "black") +
theme_map() +
coord_fixed(1.3)
mo_map

us_map + mo_map + plot_layout(ncol = 2, widths = c(1.5,1))

us_map_melvin <- ggplot() + 
  geom_polygon(data = us_missouri, 
               aes(x = long, y = lat, 
                   group = group), 
               fill = "black") +
  geom_polygon(data = usa, 
               aes(x=long, 
                   y = lat, 
                   group = group), 
               fill = NA, 
               color = "black") + 
  theme_map() +
  coord_fixed(1.3)
us_map_melvin

missouri <- map_data("county", "missouri")
mo_birth <- subset(missouri, subregion %in% c("pemiscot"))
mo_names <- subset(missouri, subregion %in% c("madison", "cole"))
missouri_melvin <- ggplot()+
  geom_polygon(data = mo_birth,
               aes(x = long,
                   y = lat,
                   group = group),
               fill = "black")+
  geom_polygon(data = mo_names,
               aes(x = long,
                   y = lat,
                   group = group),
               fill = "gray")+
  geom_polygon(data = missouri,
               aes(x = long,
                   y = lat,
                   group = group),
               fill = NA,
               color = "black")+
  theme_map()+
  coord_fixed(1.3)
missouri_melvin

us_map_melvin + missouri_melvin + plot_layout(ncol = 2, widths = c(1.5,1))

bigfoot <- filter(bigfoot,
                  long >= min_long & long <= max_long,
                  lat >= min_lat & lat <= max_lat) %>% 
  sample_n(300) %>% 
  mutate(name = "Gigantopithecus")
